及相對於未干預下，若政府採取社會最適之補貼，可消弭多少原先未干預
下之效率損失？（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ade5d61ede79", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111050", "c": "306", "s": "0904", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "公共經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-00195', 'disabled-0a2fc18c', 'disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-111-98fbe395', 'sub-disabled-0a2fc18c-01', NULL, 'essay', '我國一般商品之消費稅課徵方式採用 5%之營業稅率，依據加值型及非加
